n who is dating Satoshi's colleague, an office lady. Although it is a dream that cannot come true after all, my feelings for Furukawa, who does his job in a cool manner, grows stronger every day.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2976,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/nRDl1RbJZa9N2VmNkVzVy1NThHv.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-17","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"せつないかもしれない","original_language":"ja"},{"id":779677,"adult":false,"title":"Banned: Woman's Secret Pictures","video":false,"overview":"A man spies on an upper class woman having an illicit affair and blackmails her for sex. But she’s not the delicate flower that she appears to be.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3258,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/wo8sXpAwI6npGMslDtBcYElckeq.jpg","release_date":"1983-12-02","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":"/A37WqjwfoztYz1dgjhFlc7ic959.jpg","original_title":"発禁　秘画のおんな","original_language":"ja"},{"id":265886,"adult":false,"title":"Dark Secrets","video":false,"overview":"A woman convinces her boyfriend to go to couple therapy with her friend's and things go downhill from there.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.311,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/92fhTOYnAw7FXfaFd1ZeMwvXpGM.jpg","release_date":"2012-12-08","vote_average":3.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Dark Secrets","original_language":"en"},{"id":435997,"adult":false,"title":"Tandem","video":false,"overview":"The story of two men, one middle aged one mid twenties, who make friends and exchange cigarettes and stories of their sex lives, unaware they have unwittingly exchanged partners. The story, told in flashbacks, as the two men travel through the night on a motorcycle, is loaded with highly charged eroticism. Sex and violence are juxtaposed against the drabness of the men's everyday lives, effectively blurring the line between what is real and what is fantasy. Founded on the well-known myth of furtive sexual gropers on the rush-hour Tokyo commuter trains, Tandem is a low-key masterpiece of Japanese Pink Cinema.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.7107,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/vjvlFiDERMc7tmVYgrzYlilPbAm.jpg","release_date":"1994-03-31","vote_average":4.1,"backdrop_path":"/pw1ITFYgHDsn4qY2mtkJ8LeiWPl.jpg","original_title":"痴漢電車人妻篇　奥様は痴女","original_language":"ja"},{"id":436019,"adult":false,"title":"Good Girl","video":false,"overview":"Boon-nyeo is a nice girl who works to pay off the debt her father left behind before he disappeared. The only light in her miserable life is Kang, the teacher at the house she keeps. Then one day, co-worker Myeong-joon confesses his love for her and goes after her body. However, she enjoys the intimacy of skin touching skin. She thinks about Myeong-joon's hands but she's not satisfied. In the end, she starts to seduce Man-gap, the richest man in the market, Cheon-soo, a man working for him and Kang who she has longed for so long...","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.6947,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/s4AunUN05AuuYkBjJtxsTDdH9V3.jpg","release_date":"2015-03-25","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/cm9whEZczUOYUNoo47pxnF9qiWc.jpg","original_title":"착한 여자","original_language":"ko"},{"id":436136,"adult":false,"title":"Actress Sex Scandal 2","video":false,"overview":"Jeong-hwa has sex with various sponsors to maintain her popularity in the show biz where sexual favors are a must to survive. However, her schedules get cancelled while she goes out giving more sexual favors. Then she meets Yuni who became a celebrity because of Jeong-hwa and she tells Yuni what to do to survive in the show biz...","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.4856,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/dN6wL9QhcXn6EGmTikCmZzgOP6T.jpg","release_date":"2016-11-22","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":"/9jD8tKfc3aPq61YMxpgr8UjEHib.jpg","original_title":"여배우 섹스 스캔들 2","original_language":"ko"},{"id":437077,"adult":false,"title":"Coconut Clash","video":false,"overview":"Rie, who moved to Tokyo from a rural mining town and is penniless after being cheated by her boyfriend,